    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Hepatomancy is a FPS roguelike. Delve deep in an ever shifting temple complex. Learn the esoteric secrets of the ruins and their inhabitants, and do your best to reach the inner-most chamber. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >  </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>RANDOMLY GENERATED FLOORS</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Familiar, yet always different, the only sure way is down. Navigate the connected rooms of the cursed temple, stumble through generated levels, discover new areas and reveal ancient secrets.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>A STRANGE PATH</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >While the way down is very obvious, it is perhaps not the only one, or even the best one. The temple is full of secrets, and some artifacts might just lead you somewhere new.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Features</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>procedurally generated levels</i></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>first person action roguelike</i></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>impactful items</i></p></li></ul>",
